    "body": "@davidkna That was part of the issue, thanks! As I was in a docker container (debian:bookworm), some locales weren't set correctly and thus, leading to some errors. \r\nI just installed the `locales` pkg and ran `localedef -i en_US -c -f UTF-8 -A /usr/share/locale/locale.alias en_US.UTF-8`. Everything worked perfectly! Thanks for leading me on this ^^",
